Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:32.00,Spica - Title,,0,0,0,,Memory of a Distant Day
Comment: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:54.00,Spica - Title,,0,0,0,,Eyecatch
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.98,0:24:35.98,Spica - Title,,0,0,0,,Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.00,0:25:00.01,Spica - Title,,0,0,0,,My Mother's Face
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.09,0:01:53.92,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,My dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.92,0:01:56.67,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Year 1, Class 1, Kamogawa Asumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.51,0:02:01.68,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,My dream is to become a rocket driver!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.05,0:02:06.68,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That's because I've heard that the Earth is very pretty when you look at it from space.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:11.19,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,So I want to become a rocket driver and go into space!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.86,0:02:15.19,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I want to take people to all sorts of different planets!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.32,0:02:19.20,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,And when they're on my rocket...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:23.70,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...my dad and Lion-san will get special free rides!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.45,0:02:25.58,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,The end!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.47,0:02:45.89,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,W-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:47.27,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Why dominoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:50.19,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,These have nothing to do with being an astronaut!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:53.11,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's no good. This is complete nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.48,0:02:55.73,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What's in this box?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:02.57,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I should've known...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:06.87,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Use all of the dominoes in the boxes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:09.96,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...to make a domino line ready to be toppled within the seven days allotted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:12.50,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What? With all of these!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.13,0:03:14.92,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:17.76,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,What are they trying to make us do with this exam?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:20.13,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,They want to make us line up dominoes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.47,0:03:22.72,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.35,0:03:25.22,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:27.64,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,So that's what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:33.19,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Asumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:38.78,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,Lion-san told me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.44,0:03:44.07,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,The most important qualities for an astronaut to have...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:46.78,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,...are perseverance and a cooperative spirit, little one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.16,0:03:50.79,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,They must be trying to test those here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:58.50,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Hey now, Asumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:04:01.34,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me this thing has gotten to you already?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:02.97,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That's not it, Kei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:05.18,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It just got a little fun for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.59,0:04:07.68,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What? Fun!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.35,0:04:10.18,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. Very!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:14.90,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Asumi, you really are a strange one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:15.94,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:19.23,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,No there's no need to apologize, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:24.20,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You think this is going to be fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:38.04,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.09,0:04:43.09,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:44.93,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Is this some sort of emergency?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:49.76,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It's probably just time for lights out, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:53.35,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,What? If that's all, they should say so before turning out the lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:58.31,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Now then... Asumi, where do you wanna sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:05:00.90,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I'm fine with whatever is left after you two choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:04.53,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Well then, sorry, but could you let me take the bottom bunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:08.07,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I'm really bad about sleeping in high places.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:11.37,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, which one do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:23.38,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Really, she could at least answer us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:29.26,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I dunno how to put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:33.35,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...but these beds are so compressed that it's almost hard to breathe in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:34.85,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:38.27,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, you know, we still haven't heard her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:39.36,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:40.90,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:43.28,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It would be hard to ask now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:44.86,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Should we just give her a nickname?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:46.61,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Think about it, Asumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:51.08,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Well... her hairpin is cute, so how about Pinko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:54.24,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Pinko!? That's a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.24,0:05:56.00,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Isn't there anything else we could use?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:05:58.92,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Ukita Marika.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:02.04,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I won't say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:06.59,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Right. Then, how should we address you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.22,0:06:10.97,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Whatever. You can use my family name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.26,0:06:14.26,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Kamogawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:19.73,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What did you mean when you said that there was no way that you would be wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.35,0:06:22.06,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, what do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:24.23,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,The room number.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:27.74,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,There's no way I could be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:31.74,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,At that time, you didn't hesitate at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:33.78,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.78,0:06:39.62,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You know, all of the numbers written on the rooms are distances to stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.71,0:06:45.25,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,This room is the distance to my favorite star...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.34,0:06:51.22,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,The distance to Spica, which Lion-san told me long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:53.64,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,350 light years.{Wikipedia says it's 260 ± 20 ly actually}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:57.85,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Ah, I found Spica!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:07:00.56,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Wow. Very well done, little one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:04.65,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,It's out there, 350 light years away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:10.40,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,That's right. Shining so beautifully that it was also known as the "pearl star."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:13.87,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,It's the alpha star in the constellation Virgo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:16.66,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,But there's a secret behind that star.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.66,0:07:17.62,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:22.04,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Actually, Spica isn't just one star...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:23.92,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,...it's something called a binary star.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:25.13,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Binary star?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:27.75,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Yes, a binary star.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.75,0:07:33.39,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Two stars rotate around, chasing each other at incredible speeds...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:38.43,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,...so if you look at it from as far away as Earth, they look like one big star.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.22,0:07:45.02,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Anyhow, their rotation speed is so high that the stars aren't perfectly circular...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.02,0:07:46.94,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,...but actually oval-shaped instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:53.78,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,The twin Spicas support each other to give birth to that radiance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:59.45,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,They'll continue on and on like that until one of them disappears.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.17,0:08:05.79,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, little one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.79,0:08:08.42,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Was that explanation too difficult for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.59,0:08:11.84,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Lion-san, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.84,0:08:14.97,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,You aren't going to disappear and go off anywhere, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.97,0:08:17.26,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,We'll always, always be together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:22.43,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I won't be going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:25.77,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,As long as there are stars up there, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.15,0:08:34.99,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,It's like I'm a princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:42.54,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Asumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:44.83,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Asumi! Asumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:49.55,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Asumi! Come on, Asumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:55.01,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It's morning, Asumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:09:00.18,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Lion-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:02.31,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Lion?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:04.69,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What are you sleep-talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.89,0:09:07.81,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Come on, stand up! Let's go wash your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.81,0:09:09.94,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,I can walk by myself, Kei-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:12.57,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Just come with me. One, two! One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:16.70,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Ukita-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.16,0:09:21.08,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.66,0:09:27.67,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,She really does rub me the wrong way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:33.34,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she's just shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:37.76,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? She's just a contrary neat-freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:41.48,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Ukita-san just kind of reminds me of someone I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.48,0:09:42.22,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:45.64,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,A friend I used to play with...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:46.69,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Just the atmosphere about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:49.19,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Kasane-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:53.32,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,I couldn't understand how she felt...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:55.69,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,...and I ended up hurting her very badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.69,0:10:00.20,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,We ended up going separate ways, so I don't know what she's doing now, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.20,0:10:04.08,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,But I think I could understand her a little bit better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:07.08,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Not with words, but with feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:12.59,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Also, it may just be coincidence that we ended up together, but since we're here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:14.76,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I'd rather be friends with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:16.55,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Both you and Ukita-san.{Kei-san, and Ukita-san both.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.18,0:10:25.27,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's get breakfast out of the way and get started on those dominoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.27,0:10:26.10,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:28.77,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Or so I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:32.36,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,But looking at how many there are,\NI can't help but feel a little depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:34.61,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Where's the paper that had the project procedures written on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:36.86,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, I have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:40.16,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Use all of the dominoes in the boxes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:42.24,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...to make a domino line ready to be toppled within the seven days allotted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:44.45,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,You are free to line them up however you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:48.25,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,However, there should be one line connecting the start and finish points.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.91,0:10:51.46,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Hm, within seven days, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:53.09,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Is there something wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:57.55,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder what we're supposed to do if we finish before then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.47,0:11:01.43,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,They wouldn't give us a project that we would finish too early!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:03.05,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,That's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.05,0:11:05.56,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Hold on, there might be something written in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:09.56,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,It's certainly true that seven days is a long time for something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:14.44,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,So that means that there must be something that won't let us finish in seven days?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.32,0:11:22.95,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Ít doesn't look like there is anything else written about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.95,0:11:25.16,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess we should just give it a shot, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:30.87,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Also, it looks like we can manually push that box into the wall there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:44.34,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,How many times does that make, Kamogawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:46.35,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:48.35,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about it, Asumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:51.39,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It was because we thought that might happen that we're lining them up separately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:52.98,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:57.32,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,When we're making them into one long line later, we'll have to be more careful though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:12:02.24,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,But really, I wish they had at least given us some stoppers too. Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.09,0:12:26.89,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,With this much done, it's looking more like we might get that break that you were talking about, Asumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:29.10,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,This isn't as big of a deal as I thought it would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.87,0:12:58.00,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Ah, this is so irritating!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:13:04.55,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Why do we have to tediously line up dominoes,\Nclosed up in a room with just us three guys!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:08.01,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't come here to do these tedious little projects!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.01,0:13:09.97,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I came here to do something bigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:13.14,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Really, you've been really obnoxious lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:15.23,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Get working on this some more, you moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:17.69,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Who's a moron, you little...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:20.11,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You with the monk haircut over there, moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:22.53,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What'd you say, you little...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:28.53,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Do you understand what will happen if you get me mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.03,0:13:33.58,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I can have you all drop out alongside me with a push of this button, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:37.46,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is it, Suzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:40.38,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Just try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:42.13,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I won't have any mercy beating the crap out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.46,0:13:44.38,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It was just a joke, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:46.68,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Don't get all scary like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:55.89,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't get so serious about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.40,0:14:02.52,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Suzuki, why did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:04.69,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You can call me Shuu, Fuchuuya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:08.95,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Suzuki, why did you want to get into this school?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.07,0:14:13.54,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I told you to call me Shuu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.54,0:14:14.79,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Don't stop working, moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.45,0:14:18.37,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Well, everyone wants to go into space, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:21.63,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,"Right?" Who are we talking about, here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:26.30,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Oh? Then why did you want to come here, Fuchuuya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:30.26,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I don't want to tell someone like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:32.22,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:35.81,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Could it be a little seagull that's the surprising reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.81,0:14:36.68,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:38.81,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.48,0:14:43.65,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,For me, it would have to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:47.82,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,The photo that Armstrong took of the first moon landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:52.28,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I got the feeling that I was on the moon myself from it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:55.20,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...and I was pretty moved by it, even as a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:59.21,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Buzz Aldrin, standing at the edge of a small crater...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.79,0:15:02.08,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Humanity's first step...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.63,0:15:05.17,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,The pale blue Earth floating above the horizon...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:09.67,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,With my personality, looking at it like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.67,0:15:12.09,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,I couldn't just leave it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:18.10,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I thought that I'd love to take my own picture of the Earth just floating up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.60,0:15:19.89,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:22.23,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Well, that's my motive, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.23,0:15:23.65,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,How about you, Asumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.65,0:15:28.86,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Ah... Going to space has been a dream of mine ever since I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.86,0:15:31.86,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I wanted to become a rocket driver!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:33.74,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,A rocket driver?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:36.41,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Call it a pilot, at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:39.87,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Someone else told me the same thing once!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.87,0:15:41.41,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Most people would say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:45.42,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Um, how about you, Ukita-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:48.71,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Why did you want to get into this school?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.71,0:15:50.05,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It has nothing to do with you, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.05,0:15:52.26,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Could you please be quiet now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:55.43,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You happen to talk a lot in your sleep, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.22,0:15:59.52,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about that, Asumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:02.89,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not bothered by a little talking in your sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.89,0:16:05.27,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I guess I really do talk a lot in my sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.27,0:16:06.65,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Just a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.65,0:16:09.11,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Really, it's nothing to worry about, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.11,0:16:13.57,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That's right. Compared to your nocturnal tooth grinding, it's pretty cute at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.28,0:16:17.70,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Asumi, do I grind my teeth at night!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:19.24,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:22.16,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You do it a little bit, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.16,0:16:23.71,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That's "a little bit"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.75,0:16:26.96,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That's the first time anyone's told me that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.96,0:16:30.01,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What a shock! Now I can never get married!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.01,0:16:32.76,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I told you to be quiet already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.63,0:16:35.89,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.68,0:16:38.01,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:04.52,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Finally halfway done, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.52,0:18:05.27,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.89,0:18:08.48,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry, that was all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.48,0:18:10.19,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,No, there's no helping it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.19,0:18:14.44,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Also, I think that they gave us seven days because they figured that things like this would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.44,0:18:15.78,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Right. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:20.74,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,But now that four days have passed,\Nthis really has gotten annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.74,0:18:23.03,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,We don't know what the weather is like outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.03,0:18:26.08,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...and I feel like the pilot who asked them to put a window in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.21,0:18:30.04,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Just what meaning is there to doing this, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:33.04,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It's useless to think there's any kind of meaning to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:38.05,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,This is just a ridiculous task that they're using to weed people out, since they had so many applicants.{This is just an overly difficult project that they're using to weed people out, since there were so many applicants.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:41.93,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You really are a dry woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.93,0:18:43.97,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,As parched as the Gobi Desert, you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:46.81,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I thought I should say something earlier...{meh}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:48.98,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...but would you start addressing me by name?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.35,0:18:53.06,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Then what do you want me to call you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:56.65,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Shall I call you Lady Marika or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:18:57.90,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You neat-freak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.66,0:19:01.66,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Kei-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:17.38,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:19.51,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Why don't you cool your head off a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:20.68,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You little...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:22.05,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,How dare you do that to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:23.55,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I only called you a neat-freak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.72,0:19:25.47,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Stop it, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:28.81,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Say that once more, why don't you?\NI won't let you off easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:32.23,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I'll say it as many times as I want, you neat-freak neat-freak neat-freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.85,0:19:34.02,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You've done it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.19,0:19:35.44,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Please, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:39.53,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,First off, whose fault do you think it was that we had to do that all over?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.23,0:19:39.53,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,Why? We should all be after the same dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.53,0:19:41.40,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I wasn't the only one to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.40,0:19:43.41,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Don't group us together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.86,0:19:43.41,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.62,0:19:52.42,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.42,0:19:56.29,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,The dominoes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:02.18,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Mist?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.80,0:20:04.89,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Ou-Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.30,0:20:06.80,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Kei-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.80,0:20:07.64,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,My teeth...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.93,0:20:09.85,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Kamogawa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.85,0:20:15.69,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,My head feels so heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.52,0:20:20.28,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,My arms and legs are going numb...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:23.53,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,My vision too... What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.49,0:20:26.91,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What in the world is going on!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.74,0:20:33.46,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I feel sick... This is not normal at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:35.21,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Something must have happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:38.71,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,This is an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.71,0:20:40.26,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,We have to push it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:41.59,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.59,0:20:43.22,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,This is a test, I'm telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:44.38,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It'll calm down in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.38,0:20:46.84,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What basis do you have for saying that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.84,0:20:48.89,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,We're not gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.89,0:20:50.72,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Of course we won't!\NI won't put up with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.89,0:20:56.15,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,So that's what it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.49,0:21:09.91,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.91,0:21:13.66,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It made your teeth hurt and made you feel sick...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.66,0:21:16.87,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,And all of our carefully lined up dominoes... gone in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:21.42,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,They probably did a sudden decompression of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:24.26,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Sudden decompression? An accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.26,0:21:26.01,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,This is another part of the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.01,0:21:27.64,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,A test? This!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.09,0:21:33.89,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,The number of collisions between spaceships and debris has been increasing each year.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.89,0:21:37.81,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,So it's not unthinkable for there to be a major accident sometime in the future anymore.
Comment: 0,0:21:38.19,0:21:43.99,Spica - Notes,,0,0,0,,Debris: The remains of anything broken down or destroyed
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.19,0:21:39.44,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Debris?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.44,0:21:43.99,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Space garbage, like abandoned satellites and parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.99,0:21:46.57,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I-I know that much at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:53.70,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,If you can't keep yourself together,\Neven under those circumstances...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.70,0:21:55.62,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...you have no business going into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.91,0:21:59.54,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,But no matter how you look at it,\Nthat's going a little too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.17,0:22:01.17,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Asumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.59,0:22:04.96,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Oh man, why are you shaking like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.42,0:22:07.34,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Asumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.34,0:22:09.64,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Asumi! Come on, Asumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.64,0:22:11.76,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Hey, come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.72,0:22:14.02,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Asumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.10,0:22:19.73,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Mo... ther...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.69,0:22:23.15,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Asumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.15,0:22:25.94,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Everyone... died...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.24,0:22:29.57,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.37,0:22:31.57,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.12,0:22:33.53,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.58,0:22:36.54,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.62,0:22:40.54,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,A memory of a day long, long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.88,0:22:49.97,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.30,0:22:52.76,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,The Lion...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.86,0:24:36.32,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.32,0:24:40.15,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know what my late mother's face looked like.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.15,0:24:43.24,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,In art class, we ended up having to draw our family's faces...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.24,0:24:46.12,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...and so I began to draw my mother's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.12,0:24:52.25,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,After all, I met my mother in a strange world where only dead people can go!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.08,0:24:57.25,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Next time on Twin Spica: My Mother's Face.